OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778778356
OL,3,CWeston-super-Mare's former lido one
OL,4,Cstep closer to redevelopment
OL,6,FEvents company Live Nation wants to
OL,7,Ftransform the derelict attraction into
OL,8,Fan outdoor music venue.
OL,10,FCouncillors have now approved an
OL,11,Fagreement for a lease to Live Nation
OL,12,Fsubject to further conditions,
OL,13,Fincluding securing planning consent
OL,14,Fand reaching an operational agreement,
OL,15,Ffollowing the completion of the
OL,16,Fvenue's major refurbishment.
OL,18,FCouncillor Mike Bell described the
OL,19,Fdecision as "a significant moment in
OL,20,Fthe history of the Tropicana".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
