FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778778356
OL,3,CWeston-super-Mare's former lido one
OL,4,Cstep closer to redevelopment
OL,6,F"This decision is great news and a
OL,7,Fsignificant step forward in the
OL,8,Frebirth of the Tropicana. We know
OL,9,Fthere is more work to be done, but I'm
OL,10,Fpleased councillors agreed tonight to
OL,11,Fprogress with our preferred operator
OL,12,FLive Nation leasing the Tropicana from
OL,13,Fthe council for the next 25 years," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
