CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778778356
OL,3,CWeston-super-Mare's former lido one
OL,4,Cstep closer to redevelopment
OL,6,FEddie Kemsley, Senior Vice President
OL,7,Fof Boutique Events UK for Live Nation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are very excited to be
OL,9,Fworking with North Somerset Council to
OL,10,Fbring the Tropicana back to life with
OL,11,Fa programme of music and live events
OL,12,Ffrom 2028.
OL,14,F"We look forward to working with local
OL,15,Fbusinesses, stakeholders and members
OL,16,Fof the public and community in the
OL,17,Fcoming months to ensure a successful
OL,18,Fand happy start to this next chapter
OL,19,Ffor the venue."
OL,26,@pD@GOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
